AIML testing ground

analysis_aiml.C can read solid_gemc single particle sim output root file and write csv text file ready for AIML code.
It can take the two Cherenkov detectors "lgc", "hgc" or combined LGC and EC "lgcec"

analysis_aiml_bg_PVDIS_LD2.C and analysis_aiml_bg_SIDIS_He2.C can read solid_gemc beam background output root file and write csv text file ready for background merging in analysis_aiml.C

See example in script "getplot"

dir "hgc" has old hgc
